### ğŸ’¡ **Summary Table (IaaS vs PaaS vs SaaS)**

| Feature              | **IaaS**               | **PaaS**              | **SaaS**                |
| -------------------- | ---------------------- | --------------------- | ----------------------- |
| **You manage**       | OS, runtime, app, data | App, data             | Only data & users       |
| **Provider manages** | Hardware, networking   | Hardware, OS, runtime | Everything else         |
| **Example**          | Azure VM               | Azure App Service     | Microsoft 365           |
| **Use case**         | Full control           | Develop apps easily   | Use ready-made software |

